metadata.name: Yokozuna WRSTLR
metadata.description: YokozunaWRSTLR by Yamashita Makoto. Rikishi力士 the sumo wrestler. means gentleman of strength. Place your Rikishi against other Rikishi in Yokozuna Wrestler. web3 browser base pvp game Each Rikishi can be leveled up with gameplay and additional nft.
